{"tid":60640,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"除你以外 我已經冇法再愛另一個","createTime":"2016-12-30T15:06:25.000Z","updateTime":"2016-12-31T14:29:50.000Z","uid":2154,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"d62006352254d9d8e541b4e5fc1874adb9aaf09a","tid":60640,"uid":2154,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-30T15:06:25.000Z","msg":"講下我自己背景先 我同我第二個ex 分左分之後就愛唔到第二個<br />\n其實最慘唔係未拍到拖 而係你知道除左佢之外 你冇法再愛下一個 而佢永遠都唔會再喺你身邊<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/19.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\nI miss you"},{"pid":"8b102cd8fec352b374333476eb8e464626ab86f0","tid":60640,"uid":13835,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-30T15:17:31.000Z","msg":"一路向北？<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/42.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"242b4e1e810c092739a01a0ffb5908a19c9747c1","tid":60640,"uid":2154,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-30T15:40:26.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>一路向北？<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/42.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n咩係一路向北<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"83d7c59acda29ad36900e805cb008ed3242b877a","tid":60640,"uid":2154,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-30T15:42:30.000Z","msg":"其實我每一日都好後悔 但我卻無能為力<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/18.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"eee6c8d3cfc1e11413b4c37e0f162458b9958c97","tid":60640,"uid":2154,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-30T16:10:31.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/18.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/18.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/18.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/18.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c66316e80c92455860527762fc185a30e2752ce6","tid":60640,"uid":13835,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-30T16:41:01.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>一路向北？<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/42.png\" class=\"hkgmoji