s=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8f0b9bd11a3a84b40d102b9f24facb3139f87fab","tid":60640,"uid":2154,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-30T17:45:20.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>Yes<br />\n好似遇幾多人都好 都唔會心動<br />\n只係會更加掛住佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n其實真係好似係被詛咒咁 <br />\n我不能忘記你<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/05.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n我都覺得自己被詛咒<br />\n無論去邊做咩都好 都會心諗 如果你係度就好 又或者見到某d野就會心諗 平時一見到一定會打俾你同你講姐<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n絲打你係咪分左手之後都未試過開心<br />\n我係 我真係未試過真既開心 假笑就有"},{"pid":"cb2414c0d8b886daa15c9783f02511584f09125c","tid":60640,"uid":61839,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-30T17:47:01.000Z","msg":"點解分手先？"},{"pid":"8401d909966582d07d5c7cc505828becdd9ef038","tid":60640,"uid":2154,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-30T17:48:12.000Z","msg":"有時去返以前一齊嗰陣經過既地方 諗起以前天真啲玩 真係即時會心微笑<br />\n不過下一秒就sad返哂"},{"pid":"490f465f52a37e151d4e0901db232975a7b6370d","tid":60640,"uid":2154,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-30T17:49:55.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>點解分手先？</blockquote><br />\n因為佢父母好重視佢 而我又廢又公屋仔 久而久之 過左二年就分左"},{"pid":"8eeffc0527244a14be283b0064330011f0aa661d","tid":60640,"uid":27400,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-30T17:54:12.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>有時去返以前一齊嗰陣經過既地方 諗起以前天真啲玩 真係即時會心微笑<br />\n不過下一秒就sad返哂</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n回憶總是美好<br />\n差唔多好多地方都有同佢既影子<br />\n好耐冇大癲大肺咁笑住過一日啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5375e54dd9032a0ead31ef2eeaad26b6ebe8d359","tid":60640,"uid":60491,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-30T17:59:23.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><br />\n<br />\n其實真係好似係被詛咒咁 <br />\n我不能忘記你<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/05.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n我都覺得自己被詛咒<br />\n無論去邊做咩都好 都會心諗 如果你係度就好 又或者見到某d野就會心諗 平時一見到一定會打俾你同你講姐<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n絲打你係咪分左手之後都未試過開心<br />\n我係 我真係未試過真既開心 假笑就有</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 我又無乜記性<br />\n但同佢一齊就真係好自然 同其他人一齊就硬係周身唔自在咁"},{"pid":"e0c91d41d6aa073e5a5ada69f80b068b2a115429","tid":60640,"uid":2154,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-30T18:00:39.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>有時去返以前一齊嗰陣經過既地方 諗起以前天真啲玩 真係即時會心微笑<br />\n不過下一秒就sad返哂</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n回憶總是美好<br />\n差唔多好多地方都有同佢既影子<br />\n好耐冇大癲大肺咁笑住過一日啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n重點係你知道你永遠唔會放得低佢 而你又永遠唔會去返以前<br />\n最後 只能註定成為遺憾"},{"pid":"173e6f1bf47bd52b737f5ddf75ffed8089aacb02","tid":60640,"uid":2154,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-30T18:01:59.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n我都覺得自己被詛咒<br />\n無論去邊做咩都好 都會心諗 如果你係度就好 又或者見到某d野就會心諗 平時一見到一定會打俾你同你講姐<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n絲打你係咪分左手之後都未試過開心<br />\n我係 我真係未試過真既開心 假笑就有</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 我又無乜記性<br />\n但同佢一齊就真係好自然 同其他人一齊就硬係周身唔自在咁</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n其實我覺得拍拖最好就係舒服"},{"pid":"cdcadd6271976dae18c04ee8a042c1c372bab18c","tid":60640,"uid":22752,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-30T18:21:55.000Z","msg":"我又唔係一定非佢不可<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n只係分左手後變到唔識再去愛人咁 <br />\n點都上唔到心 搵唔返個種感覺<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"833b8ec4166bd294adb7d075dcef72731577bf2d","tid":60640,"uid":2154,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-30T18:24:29.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>我又唔係一定非佢不可<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n只係分左手後變到唔識再去愛人咁 <br />\n點都上唔到心 搵唔返個種感覺<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n雖然話唔上心就唔會太痛 但同時你都唔會享愛到愛人既感覺"},{"pid":"65e8f5eed44d908e6bb29b85675eaafbd4dc85b6","tid":60640,"uid":41662,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-30T18:25:54.000Z","msg":"我都覺 就好似身邊嘅人如果唔係佢既話根本就無意思<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/want_die.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d1f85c807a76d7370b6e39abe0874b4e18fb2549","tid":60640,"uid":2154,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-30T18:30:21.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>我都覺 就好似身邊嘅人如果唔係佢既話根本就無意思<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/want_die.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\nForever alone <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/16.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8bb07d8b8199092f32f8f74d8578ee68c04db39f","tid":60640,"uid":41662,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-30T18:41:52.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>我都覺 就好似身邊嘅人如果唔係佢既話根本就無意思<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/want_die.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\nForever alone <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/16.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/lomore_hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"905e3b46b9b800f7a5e86b5c4a0e6ebf13ed5416","tid":60640,"uid":22711,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-30T18:48:23.000Z","msg":"我都係<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ff3a450df90c7b5f4f65ceda6ef1489cad7dbd40","tid":60640,"uid":43657,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-30T18:55:24.000Z","msg":"幾年之後咪又拖住另一個<br />\n見到你個topic名都打左個冷震"}]}